race.description: Girls Day Out On Sale Soon Handicap (Bm70)
race.comment: DIAMOND EPIC (7) is a consistent conveyance who has hit the top five in 11 of her 12 starts to date and that culminated with a dominant victory over this track and trip last time out. Doesn't know how to put in a poor one and will run her usual honest race. AKKADIAN EMPEROR (3) is a stayer resuming but has won when fresh before and gets a bunch of weight relief with the 3kg claim. Should be attacking the line strongly. SANCTUARY STORM (12) has been right there in all four runs this preparation including a win over this mile journey three back. Include in calculations. VOS SAVANT (11) is a last-start winner who shouldn't be slept on.
